cetus.hir
Class Tools

java.lang.Object
  cetus.hir.Tools

public final class Tools
extends java.lang.Object

Collection of static tools that are useful in writing passes. The original set of tools since v1.1 has been separated into four different classes - SymbolTools, PrintTools, IRTools, and Tools: - SymbolTools: symbol access and management. - PrintTools : printing utilities. - IRTools : Cetus IR tools for search and manipulation. - Tools : general tools not specific to Cetus. Accessing the old utility methods through Tools class is still possible but it is deprecated As of release 1.2; use the new tools in DataFlowTools, IRTools, PrintTools, or SymbolTools.
